{
  "text": "where the function u(\u03c4 i ) is chosen appropriately depending upon whether the goal is to minimize total power or energy. Regardless of this choice, the optimization problem remains convex and hence can be efficiently solved using known algorithms [CITATION_1] . Clearly the power and energy optimal allocations are in general different for TDMA.",
